originalSql:
SELECT 
    s.s_name AS supplier_name,
    p.p_name AS part_name,
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_available_quantity,
    AVG(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS average_price_after_discount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) AS total_orders,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) AS unique_customers,
    SUBSTRING(p.p_comment, 1, 10) AS short_comment
FROM 
    supplier s
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
JOIN 
    part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN 
    lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey
JOIN 
    orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN 
    customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
WHERE 
    s.s_nationkey = (SELECT n.n_nationkey FROM nation n WHERE n.n_name = 'USA')
    AND l.l_shipdate BETWEEN DATE '1997-01-01' AND DATE '1997-12-31'
GROUP BY 
    s.s_name, p.p_name, ps.ps_availqty, l.l_extendedprice, l.l_discount, o.o_orderkey, c.c_custkey, p.p_comment
ORDER BY 
    total_available_quantity DESC, average_price_after_discount DESC

SELECT COALESCE("t6"."SUPPLIER_NAME", "t6"."SUPPLIER_NAME") AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", "t6"."PART_NAME", "t6"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", "t6"."AVERAGE_PRICE_AFTER_DISCOUNT", "t6"."TOTAL_ORDERS", "t6"."UNIQUE_CUSTOMERS", "t6"."SHORT_COMMENT"
FROM (SELECT MIN("supplier"."s_name") AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", MIN("s1"."p_name") AS "PART_NAME", SUM("partsupp"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", AVG("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) AS "AVERAGE_PRICE_AFTER_DISCOUNT", COUNT(DISTINCT "orders"."o_orderkey") AS "TOTAL_ORDERS", COUNT(DISTINCT "customer"."c_custkey") AS "UNIQUE_CUSTOMERS", MIN(SUBSTRING("s1"."p_comment", 1, 10)) AS "SHORT_COMMENT"
FROM "supplier"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "partsupp"."ps_partkey" = "s1"."p_partkey"
INNER JOIN "lineitem" ON "s1"."p_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey"
INNER JOIN "customer" ON "orders"."o_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"
WHERE "supplier"."s_nationkey" = (((SELECT "n_nationkey" AS "N_NATIONKEY"
FROM "nation"
WHERE "n_name" = 'USA'))) AND "lineitem"."l_shipdate" >= DATE '1997-01-01' AND "lineitem"."l_shipdate" <= DATE '1997-12-31'
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_name", "s1"."p_name", "partsupp"."ps_availqty", "lineitem"."l_extendedprice", "lineitem"."l_discount", "orders"."o_orderkey", "customer"."c_custkey", "s1"."p_comment"
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST, 4 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t6"
